    "name": "Little Resort Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3323050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxed first person simulator where you manage a little hotel / resort by the beach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start by renovating and customize the customer's room furniture to your taste, then the first customers will start appearing at the reception.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the profits you can unlock more Rooms so you can expand the number of Customer's your resort can have</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also in very little time you will start unlocking more facilities in the resort, where you can do varied things like give massages, serve drinks, have a stockable eating area, throw the lifeguard buoy to the customers having trouble swimming in the ocean. Unlocking each facility increases the variety of the gameplay, so each day you can do different things in a relaxed way</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modifying the Customer's room furniture</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323050/extras/9b461b48ff9aa330ce5ab1be4d2411c0.avif?t=1742547751\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cleaning the Customer's room at the start of the day</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the customers have been checked in at the Reception, and spent a day at your hotel you will need to clean their rooms at the start of the day, by picking the dirty towels, cleaning the floor stains, restocking the room's clean towels and lastly make their beds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323050/extras/68644a10008a68347e078f2df5c1d79e.avif?t=1742547751\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Making drinks at the bar</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlocking the Bar allows you to make multiple  drink types and serve them to your Customers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323050/extras/d0e4febb79d365f284f0011ca717d7b5.avif?t=1742547751\" width=616 height=866 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Swimming pool</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Swimming pool can be unlocked / repaired, so your customers can enjoy getting some sun and rest on the swimming pool chairs, and in return you get every day extra profit per Customer's Room</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323050/extras/3fb10162d4fd2cda5c203993c0d9afe1.avif?t=1742547751\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stocking food at the Eating area</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the unlockable Eating Area you can order food supplies, after they arrive in cardboard boxes just outside the building you can store them and stock the food on the food boards in the eating area</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323050/extras/ff2e36ee053365c88e752561219602b0.avif?t=1742547751\" width=616 height=692 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Giving massages to Customers at the Massage Parlor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the unlockable Massage Parlor, you can give massages to the sore Customers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323050/extras/1939312e8b9d2bcfac60b9e7374512eb.avif?t=1742547751\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Helping out Customers that are having trouble swimming by throwing a Buoy at them</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the beach you can unlock the Lifeguard Buoy, and if the Customers are having trouble swimming in the Ocean you can throw the buoy at them</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323050/extras/9aa907aa809efa331a830296e984ae84.avif?t=1742547751\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p>",
